Global Open Source Scanning Market Insights
Open Source Scanning Market size was valued at USD 5.1 Billion in 2022 and is projected to reach USD 10.8 Billion by 2030, growing at a CAGR of 9.8% from 2024 to 2030.

Open Source Scanning Market Overview
The open source scanning market is anticipated to grow significantly, with a projected market value of USD 1.5 billion in 2025, increasing at a compound annual growth rate (CAGR) of 15% from 2021 to 2025. This growth is driven by the increasing use of open source software in various industries and the rising concerns regarding cybersecurity risks. Open source scanning tools are crucial for identifying vulnerabilities, license compliance issues, and security risks in open source code. The expanding adoption of DevOps practices and continuous integration/continuous delivery (CI/CD) pipelines further accelerates the demand for open source scanning solutions.

